    "description": "If you're a passionate Consultant Physician with drive and ambition, Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions in Patna is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions:\nIpca Laboratories Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions!",
